	<div class="article-detail-bd">
			<div class="excerpt">
				两种风格，各有千秋。
			</div>
		<div class="detail">
				<!-- 普通文章 -->
				<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;">
	法国巴黎有一个单亲家庭，一位年轻的父亲带着年幼的儿子一起生活。他们邀请了设计师&nbsp;<a href="http://www.glennmedioni.com/">Glenn Medioni</a>&nbsp;，<a href="http://www.contemporist.com/2015/09/21/an-apartment-in-paris-designed-for-a-father-and-his-son/" target="_blank">将自己的家打造成了风格截然不同的两个空间。</a> 
</p>
<p>
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/fc5fd909d0b1.jpg" width="640" height="428" title="父与子的房间对比" alt="父与子的房间对比" /> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<span>父与子的房间风格对比</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/3b7bb8fd0671.jpg" width="640" height="426" title="儿子的空间" alt="儿子的空间" /><span>儿子的空间</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/1c0e55fd8823.jpg" width="640" height="426" title="父亲的小客厅" alt="父亲的小客厅" /><span>餐厅</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/21b867a86442.jpg" width="640" height="426" title="父亲的卧室" alt="父亲的卧室" /><span>父亲的卧室</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/2de6744fe16f.jpg" width="640" height="426" title="差距" alt="差距" /><span>反差</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/33323f39da57.jpg" width="640" height="426" title="儿子的区域" alt="儿子的区域" /><span>儿子的区域</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/7a52b741c257.jpg" width="640" height="426" title="双人床铺" alt="双人床铺" />儿童床铺<span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/ae6bdd878664.jpg" width="640" height="426" title="细节" alt="细节" /><span>细节</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/d402fe4a0c01.jpg" width="640" height="960" title="玩具" alt="玩具" /><span>玩具</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/ee358e9d3618.jpg" width="640" height="960" title="父亲的洗手间" alt="父亲的洗手间" /><span>父亲的洗手间</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/47901a50a8e5.jpg" width="640" height="426" title="洗手间" alt="洗手间" /><span>洗手间</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;">
	<span>看了这些图后就一个想法：儿子长大了怎么办？再重新装修？十年恍惚一瞬间呐。<span style="text-align:left;">设计师&nbsp;</span><a href="http://www.glennmedioni.com/">Glenn Medioni</a><span style="text-align:left;">&nbsp;还设计过其他作品，比如下图中的这个室内设计：</span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/ba8bd188dcee.jpg" width="640" height="337" title="另外一处住宅" alt="另外一处住宅" /><span>另外一处住宅</span> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
